# Commit message template (en-AU)
# Use this as your repository commit template. It uses Australian English and present-tense verbs.
# Example:
#   fix(pages/about.html): remove malformed meta characters and close head tags
#
# Template:
<type>(scope): short summary

Detailed description (why), additional notes, and any manual review required.

# Commit types (one-line convention)
# fix — bug fix
# feat — new feature
# docs — documentation only changes
# chore — maintenance tasks, tooling, or build changes
# refactor — code changes that do not change behaviour